Time":"2019-02-25T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"好撚難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2421f42ed9dbc35548c037e1fe03d6fa6152ae","tid":1034413,"uid":10583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"分上下集出已經反映當時作品既人氣<br />\n以前無上網同Youtube，要玩Game先知出招動畫<br />\n而家唔使買Game都可以睇Youtube<br />\n隻Game真係全Fans向了"},{"pid":"1b62d30ac88609613c4e32565760661ad5ca3136","tid":1034413,"uid":111955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fc549PD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffc549PD.png&h=b05f93d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"828d7cf69a1afa2cbd54a254ba2a05da49a36dfe","tid":1034413,"uid":90259,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"F係童年回憶，但成隻game根本on9<br />\n應該改名富野由悠季大戰<br />\n個編劇都唔知有冇睇過光頭佬以外嘅卡通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n9成敵人係保士達、拜士頓同高達系、後期多個巴夫克蘭又係富野<br />\n初參戰嘅W，9成時間係敵人仲要廢到喊<br />\n飛越顛峰、超獸機神、三一萬能俠連佢地班敵人都失埋踪<br />\nEVA根本每關都係劇情關<br />\n細個玩真係好無癮，W同EVA播完冇耐，隻驚封面有佢地但故事入面隱左形咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有角色唔平衡到弱智，真實系唔係NT根本冇人權<br />\n克莉絲巴尼哥奧果啲係廢鳩冇問題，達巴希羅都屎到仆街係咩料？故事入面佢地係強者，喺F入面就俾人當狗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次就係玩F，但隻驚本身真係好廢"},{"pid":"37b6a085e4d8ea583e75bd367eef86d3a5993887","tid":1034413,"uid":198866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"伍索，多蒙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5539824ab75dd0c5222c28a2ee05cedbc3c928","tid":1034413,"uid":112813,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"好玩，尤其係鐘意真實系既，但正如上面巴打講平衡做得唔好，成堆nt高達清場，超級系二回行動遲執雞都嫌行得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWing用返原著設定黎講的確係敵人，wing 個5隻老妖叫5架高達去打爆聯邦解放殖民星，咁岩自己友就係聯邦入面既隆巴納隊，唔做敵人先怪. Wing 既設定機勁人廢， wzc 300運動性勁到飛天，招炮又大力，可惜希羅能力設定得太廢<br />\n<br />\n超級系堆boss被堆nt撚狗咁撚，但原創堆boss真係有絕望感，細個打淨係識走，大個打返先識善用挑撥+脫力計好每一步打"},{"pid":"3256dd0ca9f05957f1e8f7aa02610578dfcb3ac7","tid":1034413,"uid":174530,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"咁多集一定係F最好玩，起碼叫有啲難度，其他我阿媽都識爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過神高達太強，又大力，敵人又永遠打佢唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c869b0930d51ce7060e014e09502e3e6c2850066","tid":1034413,"uid":64193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"最記得 打白卡難打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初號機暴走比白卡秒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931614b41416e874da86ea1a9a353f4f425f9fe5","tid":1034413,"uid":112813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3256dd0ca9f05957f1e8f7aa02610578dfcb3ac7","tid":1034413,"uid":174530,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"咁多集一定係F最好玩，起碼叫有啲難度，其他我阿媽都識爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過神高達太強，又大力，敵人又永遠打佢唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"巴打你鐘意難打既話推介你打gba版既og2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好話boss, 就咁堆兵都已經勁到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n量產型W<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24f6e2e209dfd792677606b3628dde289f01ee3","tid":1034413,"uid":52087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"F 同FF之外最難過一定係Alpha外傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eea814c7f8ba11b0982cc84544fc0e29ab6d177","tid":1034413,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"931614b41416e874da86ea1a9a353f